  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this study is to investigate neuronal differences (EEG/evoked potentials; functional
      MRI) between patients with major depression and healthy controls concerning brain activity
      after acute pain as well as changes of pain related brain activity during treatment with
      escitalopram.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
